				<IHandle type="e">
					<_hm2Class type="a">IUCDiagram</_hm2Class>
					<_hid type="a">GUID e0943032-4ba9-4a3f-b899-7b04eacebd15</_hid>
				</IHandle>
			</_theMainDiagram>
			<_description type="p"><IDescription type="e">
				<_textRTF type="a">{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg1252\deff0\deflang1033{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset0 Arial;}}%0D
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\b\fs20 Pre-Condition\par%0D
\b0 1) -\par%0D
\par%0D
\b Trigger\par%0D
\b0 1) Data is polled periodically with a period of 1 minute\b\par%0D
\par%0D
Post-Condition\b0\par%0D
1) The collected data is stored in data storage\par%0D
\b\par%0D
Main Scenario\par%0D
\b0 1) New data is requested from the sensors\par%0D
2) The sensors read new data\par%0D
3) The data is send to the data storage\par%0D
4) The data is saved in the data storage\b\par%0D
\par%0D
Alternative Scenario\par%0D
\b0 1) If no connection can be established with the sensor, a connection error is raised to a maintance worker\par%0D
\par%0D
\par%0D
\par%0D
\par%0D
\par%0D
\par%0D
\par%0D
\par%0D
\par%0D
\b\par%0D
}%0D
</_textRTF>
			</IDescription>
