			<_description type="p"><IDescription type="e">
				<_textRTF type="a">{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg1252\deff0\deflang1033{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset0 Arial;}}%0D
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\b\fs20 Pre-Condition\par%0D
\b0 1) Sensor data is available in the data storage\par%0D
\par%0D
\b Trigger\par%0D
\b0 1) A researcher requests data\b\par%0D
\par%0D
Post-Condition\b0\par%0D
1) The requested data is send to a researcher\par%0D
\b\par%0D
Main Scenario\par%0D
\b0 1) A researcher requests sensor data \par%0D
2) The requested data is pulled from the data storage\par%0D
3) The requested data is send to the requesting researcher per email in the requested language\b\par%0D
\par%0D
Alternative Scenario\par%0D
\b0 1) If not all data is available in the data storage, only the available part is send and the researcher is informed that the rest is not available\par%0D
\par%0D
\par%0D
\par%0D
\par%0D
}%0D
</_textRTF>
