			<_description type="p"><IDescription type="e">
				<_textRTF type="a">{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg1252\deff0\deflang1033{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset0 Arial;}}%0D
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\b\fs20 Pre-Condition\par%0D
\b0 1) Data storage contains sensor data\par%0D
\par%0D
\b Trigger\par%0D
\b0 1) Data is requested \b\par%0D
\par%0D
Post-Condition\b0\par%0D
1) The requested data is received by the requester\par%0D
\b\par%0D
Main Scenario\par%0D
\b0 1) Data is requested\par%0D
2) The data is located in the data storage\par%0D
3) The requested data is send to the requester\b\par%0D
\par%0D
Alternative Scenario\par%0D
\b0 1) If the requested data is not available in the data storage, a notification is send to a maintance worker\par%0D
\par%0D
\par%0D
\par%0D
\par%0D
\par%0D
\par%0D
\par%0D
\par%0D
}%0D
</_textRTF>
			</IDescription>
